Class ServiceEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dhbw.ravensburg.verteiltesysteme.server.ServiceEndpoint

  • public class ServiceEndpoint
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a high level application service. It will initialize a gRPC server with a respective gRPC service implementation.
